Touch of Vitality					KEY:Dragon Shaman ~ Touch of Vitality1			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Dragon Shaman Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																						DEFINE:TouchOfVitality|0																							DESC:At 6th level, you can heal the wounds of living creatures (your own or others) by touch. Each day you can heal %1 hit points. You may choose to divide your healing among multiple recipients, and you don't have to use it all at once. Using it is a standard action.|TouchOfVitality																																																																																																																																													BONUS:VAR|TouchOfVitality|(DragonShamanLVL*2*CHA)								SOURCEPAGE:p.14
